window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>Follow the ghost</i></b><b>, they’d said. </b><b><i>It’ll be fun,</i></b><b> they said</b></p> <p>Rain, Graham, Ezra, and Warren have been on the hunt for answers for weeks after learning that Rain’s brother is alive, and that Warren played a part in his disappearance. After facing off with the demon who took Rain’s brother, all of them nearly dying in the process, the woman in black leads them to reinforcements.</p> <p>The mysterious family the woman in black brought them to is willing to help, so long as they don’t ask too many questions. Like what they are. <i>Who</i> they are.</p> <p>But Graham’s certain he knows exactly what and who they are.</p> <p>After all, he’s been praying to them his entire life.</p>"; 
